1. Ja ću *pući* od gladi ako ne pojedem nešto. (I will starve if I don't eat something.)
2. Oni su sinoć *pucale* od smeha. (They were cracking up with laughter last night.)
3. Učim kako *pucati* iz vatrenog oružja. (I am learning how to shoot firearms.)
4. Izlomio sam nogu i čujem kako mi kosti *pucaju*. (I broke my leg and I can hear my bones cracking.)
5. Vozač kamiona je *pucao* od umora i jedva je držao oči otvorene. (The truck driver was nodding off from fatigue and could barely keep his eyes open.)
6. Đaci su *puštali* zmajeve na livadi. (The students were flying kites in the meadow.)
7. Prozor je *pucao* od jakog vetra. (The window was rattling from the strong wind.)
8. U akciji je *pukao* jedan odnos državnika. (One diplomatic relationship broke down during the operation.)
9. Nismo uspeli da *puknemo* branu da bi se izlila voda. (We failed to blow up the dam to release the water.)
10. Šta se *puca* u gradu? (What's going on in the city? [in this context "puca" means "happening" or "going on"])